{"tid":461580,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你地接唔接受到另一半keep住ex嘅野","createTime":"2017-11-07T17:21:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-08T15:11:21.000Z","uid":99796,"like":6,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"f810cc49c9afd661574227294435c3cf8e434842","tid":461580,"uid":99796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T17:21:09.000Z","msg":"其實我同男朋友一齊就五年<br />\n我地中學認識 佢係大我一級嘅師兄<br />\n同佢一齊嘅時候<br />\n知道佢曾經有個鐘意咗六年但無結果嘅女仔<br />\n（其實我好佩服佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n知道佢曾經一直等一直等<br />\n仲為佢做過好多承諾<br />\n<br />\n好早同男朋友一齊嘅時候<br />\n知道佢留起咗隻公仔喺屋企<br />\n係因為未能送出<br />\n（後來我廹佢擲咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n再後來知道佢曾經有寫日記嘅習慣<br />\n雖然係英文但大約內容都係話：<br />\n喱個女仔好可愛 係個好女仔之類<br />\n（仲附上一張嗰女仔嘅相）<br />\n<br />\n喱本簿我知依家仲有keep住<br />\n我有反映過我唔鐘意本簿嘅存在<br />\n但佢始乎仲想留住本簿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我接受唔到&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢會不斷講依家得返我一個<br />\n我同佢已經無野，淨係愛你一個<br />\n但每次佢提起6年喱啲字眼<br />\n或者提起嗰女仔<br />\n<br />\n我就無辦法忘記本簿嘅存在<br />\n其實我好撚介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然話就快五年，但&hellip;<br />\n我好怕男朋友未放底佢&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好怕男朋友其實久唔久會睇返相<br />\n<br />\n我有諗過如果佢最後無法放棄嗰女仔嘅所有，不如我同佢分手&hellip;"},{"pid":"4b7665baff7b638e07c190af31757e4557d87796","tid":461580,"uid":85633,"like":17,"dislike":6,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T17:25:32.000Z","msg":"我接受唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都淨係得番我一個 <br />\n點解重要keep第2個女仔嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b706532787b827182f3b9b02976146e0506a0f35","tid":461580,"uid":74262,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T17:27:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"840c8e1a65432e071819f51cb399708759413ed3","tid":461580,"uid":85633,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T17:32:01.000Z","msg":"口講話無所謂<br />\n其實個心都係會記得 有條刺係到<br />\n佢一日唔掉我都會諗起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f35b8c9cac04c6336e582c7b09057f479e887e","tid":461580,"uid":92697,"like":36,"dislike":5,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T17:42:03.000Z","msg":"keep咪keep  除左佢日日拎出嚟回味  如果唔係收埋左嘅話又有咩問題<br />\n每個人都有過去  兩個人一齊就係講個信字<br />\n學下唔好咁執著  就會相處得開心啲"},{"pid":"8f9d58368588212945c1cab8b523c57412f67377","tid":461580,"uid":99796,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T17:48:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>keep咪keep  除左佢日日拎出嚟回味  如果唔係收埋左嘅話又有咩問題<br />\n每個人都有過去  兩個人一齊就係講個信字<br />\n學下唔好咁執著  就會相處得開心啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自問我同佢一齊<br />\n我無辦法接受佢仲keep住任何實物<br />\n我會覺得男朋友好似精神出軌咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f403cede06c310b9baccbaa8fc759889e8930fc","tid":461580,"uid":99796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T17:49:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>口講話無所謂<br />\n其實個心都係會記得 有條刺係到<br />\n佢一日唔掉我都會諗起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60b41ac32458490696296c98c2219852d7e9981","tid":461580,"uid":99796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T17:50:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>只要佢仲係處女 就算佢全屋都係ex d野都冇所謂<br />\n只要佢地冇親密到會上床呢個地步就得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個女仔係咪處我就唔知<br />\n但我肯定男朋友無同佢上床"},{"pid":"3d86b63762d311e56795c49b77e8606f29f275c7","tid":461580,"uid":32973,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T17:51:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>只要佢仲係處女 就算佢全屋都係ex d野都冇所謂<br />\n只要佢地冇親密到會上床呢個地步就得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個女仔係咪處我就唔知<br />\n但我肯定男朋友無同佢上床</blockquote><br />\n係上唔到"},{"pid":"2a6dc47bceb7761ab2ea0bc6f42b63ca3c417311","tid":461580,"uid":54836,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:04:01.000Z","msg":"比啲空間佢啦<br />\n無謂迫人扔佢覺得重要嘅野<br />\n佢都講到明依家得你<br />\n咁已經夠啦<br />\n果段回憶可能佢好珍重 唔代表佢精神出軌架喎"},{"pid":"393f11617c9f2060e196b3661ba250bc336ca283","tid":461580,"uid":123082,"like":22,"dislike":3,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:06:45.000Z","msg":"點解要佢掉左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本日記係佢寫既<br />\n回憶係佢既<br />\n你憑咩要佢掉左屬於佢自己既回憶<br />\n你係佢現任都唔代表可以咁做"},{"pid":"ccb872db9be2c67c90ef2320916b01fec9e30884","tid":461580,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:07:46.000Z","msg":"點解要咁自私破壞人地既回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153e67387ba8b81967ec9a14b98b82f058de1fe5","tid":461580,"uid":51250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:08:13.000Z","msg":"廹佢擲咗佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9f3f174011a82eb303aa1e05a194a909673b75","tid":461580,"uid":131980,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:10:55.000Z","msg":"回憶好珍貴<br />\n空間要比足<br />\n唔係正臭雞<br />\n屌你老母閪"},{"pid":"de9a7e107c0c04f97792cf6beb8ad3c8b385b42c","tid":461580,"uid":47055,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:11:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比啲空間佢啦<br />\n無謂迫人扔佢覺得重要嘅野<br />\n佢都講到明依家得你<br />\n咁已經夠啦<br />\n果段回憶可能佢好珍重 唔代表佢精神出軌架喎</blockquote><br />\n同意"},{"pid":"3ee268fd01cc719d138afbf8ba7fb32bc5dc0431","tid":461580,"uid":99796,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:12:40.000Z","msg":"依家咁樣我覺得佢好似唔係全部屬於我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就連佢開口提起我都覺得好辛苦"},{"pid":"731f811cf79b2b39870f1f90f988d6d0e2bca0ad","tid":461580,"uid":99796,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:13:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>回憶好珍貴<br />\n空間要比足<br />\n唔係正臭雞<br />\n屌你老母閪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講還講唔好講屋企人"},{"pid":"c442c5b6d95ecbc750b89386334bdfee1b005f83","tid":461580,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:14:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家咁樣我覺得佢好似唔係全部屬於我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就連佢開口提起我都覺得好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n如果成日開口提住 就有問題了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc9194bbc3162a720ef36ea831efcf1da51eddfd","tid":461580,"uid":99796,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:21:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>依家咁樣我覺得佢好似唔係全部屬於我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就連佢開口提起我都覺得好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n如果成日開口提住 就有問題了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我介意係因為覺得自己不如人<br />\n我知道佢中學有嗰女仔<br />\n條件比我好 靚過我斯文過我<br />\n到依家佢知我介意㗎<br />\n但佢仲會開住玩笑咁提起嗰女仔<br />\n<br />\n我同男朋友一齊五年<br />\n算係佢第一個女朋友<br />\n但我總會覺得自己比不上佢單戀過六年嘅女仔<br />\n<br />\n我有整相簿比佢 都知佢仲留緊本日記<br />\n有時佢同我講會睇返本相簿<br />\n我反而會諗佢其實係想睇本日記簿<br />\n睇返個女仔張相"},{"pid":"961f9bae10c6903848d09547bdfe26f913b33766","tid":461580,"uid":68258,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:22:12.000Z","msg":"唔好咁執著 諗下佢平時對你好冇<br />\n我諗呢啲係佢嘅回憶 始終咁耐係有相對紀念價值<br />\n有時可能唔係紀念對方 而係記低個陣嘅自己"},{"pid":"f86d5200c800ff9fbff409933d812bc95bddf449","tid":461580,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:23:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廹佢擲咗佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/so